title: Most Popular 2 bed/2 bath and yard
posting_body: ['Fabulous opportunity to purchase a prime 2 bedrooms/2 baths unit at Lake Park Condominium complex!', 'Simply magical and peaceful!', 'Remodeled with a light, bright airy feel.', 'Move in ready with stainless steel appliances, new dual pane window throughout, slider with pet door, window treatments with motorized shades, tile bathrooms with walk-in master shower, modern fixture, Pergo floor and plush carpet in the bedrooms, newer AC/Heat pump and ductwork.', 'Enjoy your morning coffee and stunning sunsets on the charming covered balcony.', 'A short elevator ride or stairway walk down and you will be ready to stroll the paths at Lake Murray.', 'Nature surrounds this unique property; original owner occupied for over 40 years.', 'Deeded parking space across from elevator.', 'Complex Features: Garden ponds with fountains, many water features thru out the 24acre complex.', 'Plus 5 pools,4 spas, 2 tennis courts with lights, pickle ball courts, recreation room with full kitchen, exercise room with newer equipment plus showers and saunas.', 'Resort style living close to shopping, restaurants, hiking trails, Cowles mountain trails & freeway access.']
